    title: "Papildus d\u0101vanas",
    quote: "\u201CM\u0113s redzam, k\u0101 m\u016Bsu starp\u0101 tas notiek katru dienu. \u0160\u012Bs br\u012Bnumain\u0101s p\u0101rmai\u0146as ir gar\u012Bgas atmodas pier\u0101d\u012Bjums.\u201D",
    reference: "B\u0101zes teksts, 53. lpp.",
