    title: "Bezsp\u0113c\u012Bba un person\u012Bga atbild\u012Bba",
    quote: "\u201CNesp\u0113dami uz\u0146emties atbild\u012Bbu, m\u0113s paties\u012Bb\u0101 pa\u0161i rad\u012Bj\u0101m savas probl\u0113mas.\u201D",
    reference: "B\u0101zes teksts, 14. lpp.",
