    quote: "\u201CSevis \u017E\u0113lo\u0161ana ir viens no posto\u0161\u0101kajiem tr\u016Bkumiem \u2013 t\u0101 izs\u016Bc no mums visu pozit\u012Bvo ener\u0123iju.\u201D",
    reference: "B\u0101zes teksts, 83. lpp.",
