    affirmation: "Tikai \u0161odien: Mans Augst\u0101kais Sp\u0113ks nav devis man iesp\u0113ju atvese\u013Coties, lai mani pamestu! Kad mani p\u0101r\u0146ems panika, es veik\u0161u darb\u012Bbas, lai mekl\u0113tu Dieva nebeidzam\u0101s r\u016Bpes un vad\u012Bbu."
