    quote: "\u201CSponsoram nav oblig\u0101ti j\u0101b\u016Bt draugam, ta\u010Du vi\u0146\u0161 var b\u016Bt k\u0101ds, kuram m\u0113s uzticamies. Ar sponsoru",
