    affirmation: "Tikai \u0161odien: Man ir kaut kas v\u0113rt\u012Bgs, ar ko dal\u012Bties. Es \u0161odien apmekl\u0113\u0161u sapulci un dal\u012B\u0161os sav\u0101 atvese\u013Co\u0161an\u0101s pieredz\u0113."
