    body: "Kad m\u0113s pirmo reizi nok\u013Cuv\u0101m Anon\u012Bmajos Narkom\u0101nos, daudziem no mums nebija likum\u012Bgas nodarbo\u0161an\u0101s. Atn\u0101kot uz NA programmu, ne visi no mums uzreiz nolemj, ka k\u013C\u016Bs par god\u012Bgiem un priek\u0161z\u012Bm\u012Bgiem pilso\u0146iem. Ta\u010Du atvese\u013Cojoties, m\u0113s \u0101tri atkl\u0101jam, ka nej\u016Btamies \u0113rti, darot daudzas no liet\u0101m, kuras, lieki nedom\u0101jot, dar\u012Bj\u0101m akt\u012Bvaj\u0101 lieto\u0161an\u0101. Atvese\u013Cojoties, m\u0113s s\u0101kam b\u016Bt god\u012Bgi jaut\u0101jumos, kuri, iesp\u0113jams, m\u016Bs neuztrauca, kad m\u0113s \u201Cbliez\u0101m\u201D. M\u0113s s\u0101kam atgriezt atlikumu, ko veikal\u0101 kasiere mums ir izdevusi k\u013C\u016Bdas p\u0113c, vai ar\u012B atz\u012Bstamies, kad iebraucam ielas mal\u0101 st\u0101vo\u0161\u0101 automa\u0161\u012Bn\u0101. M\u0113s saprotam, ka, ja m\u0113s varam r\u012Bkoties god\u012Bgi s\u012Bkumos, mums k\u013C\u016Bst daudz viegl\u0101k iztur\u0113t nopietn\u0101kus god\u012Bguma p\u0101rbaud\u012Bjumus. Daudzi no mums \u0161eit ierad\u0101s ar \u013Coti ierobe\u017Eotu sp\u0113ju b\u016Bt god\u012Bgiem. Tom\u0113r m\u0113s secin\u0101m, ka, str\u0101d\u0101jot ar Divpadsmit So\u013Ciem, m\u016Bsu dz\u012Bve s\u0101k main\u012Bties. Mums vairs nav pie\u0146emami, ka m\u0113s g\u016Bstam labumu uz citu r\u0113\u0137ina, un m\u0113s varam justies labi attiec\u012Bb\u0101 uz m\u016Bsu jaunatkl\u0101to god\u012Bgumu.",
    affirmation: "Tikai \u0161odien: Es nov\u0113rt\u0113\u0161u god\u012Bguma l\u012Bmeni sav\u0101 dz\u012Bv\u0113 un paskat\u012B\u0161os, vai tas mani apmierina."
