    affirmation: "Tikai \u0161odien: Es iedom\u0101\u0161os, k\u0101da var\u0113tu b\u016Bt mana dz\u012Bve bez rakstura tr\u016Bkumiem. Es l\u016Bg\u0161u, lai Dievs b\u016Btu gatavs nov\u0113rst manus tr\u016Bkumus."
