    title: "Dz\u012Bvot ar gar\u012Bgo pieredzi",
    quote: "\u201CJa medit\u0101cijai ir v\u0113rt\u012Bba, t\u0101s rezult\u0101ti ir redzami m\u016Bsu ikdienas dz\u012Bv\u0113.\u201D",
    reference: "B\u0101zes teksts, 49. lpp.",
