    affirmation: "Tikai \u0161odien: Es pie\u0146em\u0161u, ka man nav atbildes uz visiem dz\u012Bves jaut\u0101jumiem. Neraugoties uz to, es tic\u0113\u0161u Dievam, k\u0101 es Vi\u0146u saprotu, un turpin\u0101\u0161u savu atvese\u013Co\u0161an\u0101s ce\u013Cojumu."
