    affirmation: "Tikai \u0161odien: Es cent\u012B\u0161os nostiprin\u0101t attiec\u012Bbas ar savu Augst\u0101ko Sp\u0113ku. Es zinu, ka mana Augst\u0101k\u0101 Sp\u0113ka gribas izpratne sniegs skaidr\u012Bbas, virz\u012Bbas un dv\u0113seles miera saj\u016Btu."
