    affirmation: "Tikai \u0161odien: Es r\u016Bp\u012Bgi izv\u0113rt\u0113\u0161u visus savus rakstura tr\u016Bkumus, lai atkl\u0101tu, vai esmu gatavs, lai Dievs, k\u0101 es Vi\u0146u saprotu, atbr\u012Bvo mani no tiem."
