    title: "Humora saj\u016Bta",
    quote: "\u201CM\u0113s atkl\u0101jam, ka tad, kad atbr\u012Bvojamies no aps\u0113st\u012Bbas ar sevi, m\u0113s sp\u0113jam saprast, ko noz\u012Bm\u0113 b\u016Bt laim\u012Bgiem, priec\u012Bgiem un br\u012Bviem.\u201D",
    reference: "B\u0101zes teksts, 110. lpp.",
