    title: "Turpinot atvese\u013Coties",
    quote: "\u201CPa\u0161apmierin\u0101t\u012Bba ir ienaidnieks biedriem ar lielu t\u012Br\u012Bbas laiku. Ja m\u0113s ilgu laiku esam pa\u0161apmierin\u0101ti, atvese\u013Co\u0161an\u0101s process apst\u0101jas.\u201D",
