    affirmation: "Tikai \u0161odien: Es atcer\u0113\u0161os, ka esmu dz\u012Bvs Divpadsmit\u0101 So\u013Ca piem\u0113rs. Es nevaru b\u016Bt \u201Cneveiksm\u012Bgs\u201D, m\u0113\u0123inot nest v\u0113sti citam atkar\u012Bgajam."
