    title: "Beznosac\u012Bjumu kapitul\u0101cija",
    quote: "\u201CPal\u012Bdz\u012Bba atkar\u012Bgajiem ir iesp\u0113jama tikai tad, kad sp\u0113jam atz\u012Bt piln\u012Bgu sak\u0101vi. Tas var likties bied\u0113jo\u0161i, ta\u010Du tie\u0161i \u0161is ir pamats, uz kura m\u0113s b\u016Bv\u0113jam savas dz\u012Bves.\u201D",
