    title: "Ieguld\u012Bjums",
    quote: "\u201CM\u0113s paman\u0101m savu gar\u012Bgo izaugsmi, kad k\u013C\u016Bstam sp\u0113j\u012Bgi sniegt pal\u012Bdz\u012Bbu citiem.\u201D",
