    affirmation: "Tikai \u0161odien: Es sev atg\u0101din\u0101\u0161u, ka neesmu viens, jo katr\u0101 dz\u012Bves br\u012Bd\u012B varu l\u016Bgt pal\u012Bdz\u012Bbu savam Augst\u0101kajam Sp\u0113kam."
