    dateLV: "1. decembris",
    title: "Dz\u012Bves balvas",
    quote: "\u201CM\u0113s s\u0101kam l\u016Bgt tikai izpratni par Dieva gribu attiec\u012Bb\u0101 uz mums. T\u0101d\u0101 veid\u0101 m\u0113s sa\u0146emam tikai to, ar ko esam sp\u0113j\u012Bgi tikt gal\u0101.\u201D",
    reference: "B\u0101zes teksts, 50. lpp.",
